1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
CMD: "robot turn ninety degrees to the left"

2
00:00:04,790 --> 00:00:09,790
CMD: "and continue to the farther wall"

3
00:00:32,990 --> 00:00:37,990
Robot: "I'm not sure what you mean by the farther wall.  Where should I continue to?"

4
00:00:38,110 --> 00:00:43,110
CMD: "robot continue down the hallway directly in front of you underneath the overhead light"

5
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:28,860
Robot: "I don't see an overhead light in my current position.  Would you like me to send a photo?"

6
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:30,280
CMD: "robot send a photo"

7
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:42,880
Robot: "sent"

